SEARCH
Package domain.controllers

Class DomainController

java.lang.Object
domain.controllers.DomainController
public class DomainController extends Object
Domain controller that serves as a facade for the domain layer. It manages user profiles and forms by delegating to UserController, ProfileController, and FormController.

      public DomainController(Integer profileID)

      Parameters:
